            <div class="testim-name">Mariah K.</div>
            <div class="testim-meta">Content Creator &middot; YouTube + brand sponsorship LLC &middot; Miami</div>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="testim-card">
          <div class="testim-avatar testim-avatar-2"><img src="https://i.pravatar.cc/300?img=57" alt="James R., touring musician and recording artist" width="300" height="300" loading="lazy" onerror="this.onerror=null;this.src='https://placehold.co/300x300/F0EDE8/6B5C4B/png?text=57';"></div>
          <blockquote class="testim-quote">"Streaming royalties through one LLC, touring through another, sync licensing through a third. Every lender I called said the structure was too complex. Jim pulled all three K-1s, documented the royalty pattern, and routed me through the right program."</blockquote>
          <div class="testim-attribution">
            <div class="testim-name">James R.</div>
            <div class="testim-meta">Recording Artist &middot; Touring + streaming + sync licensing &middot; Fort Lauderdale</div>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="testim-card">
          <div class="testim-avatar testim-avatar-3"><img src="https://i.pravatar.cc/300?img=58" alt="Emma S., freelance designer with retainer clients" width="300" height="300" loading="lazy" onerror="this.onerror=null;this.src='https://placehold.co/300x300/E8EFE8/3D5A3D/png?text=58';"></div>
          <blockquote class="testim-quote">"Twelve 1099s, four retainers, one Schedule C with a lot of legitimate deductions. The first lender ran me through automated underwriting and declined. Jim built the file manually using two years of bank statements. Closed in 32 days."</blockquote>
          <div class="testim-attribution">
            <div class="testim-name">Emma S.</div>
            <div class="testim-meta">Freelance Designer &middot; Retainer + project mix &middot; Coral Gables</div>
          </div>
